表格会员的代码预览

drop table if exists user;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: user */
/*==============================================================*/
create table user
(
用户id int not null auto_increment,
pmpid int,
username varchar(50),
usermm varchar(50),
usersfz varchar(50),
userdh varchar(50),
userdz varchar(50),
useryzbh varchar(50),
usersf int,
userwt varchar(50),
userda varchar(50),
primary key (用户id)
);

alter table user add constraint FK_Relationship_1 foreign key (pmpid)
references pmp (pmpid) on delete restrict on update restrict;
